{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Recover debt from elsewhere in the EU"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/recover-debt-from-elsewhere-in-european-union.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/recover-debt-from-elsewhere-in-european-union"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B77","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Debt recovery if you're owed money from people or businesses in another EU country - how to ask for a repayment","updated_at":"2012-10-08T17:04:49+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>If you\u2019re owed money by someone in another EU country, you can recover the debt using internationally-recognised court forms.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This is known as making a &lsquo;cross-border&rsquo; claim. You will have to pay a court fee.</p>\n\n<h2>If they admit owing the money</h2>\n\n<p>If the other person or business admits owing the money, you can make a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://e-justice.europa.eu/content_european_payment_order-41-eu-en.do\" title=\"European Payment Order\">European Order for Payment.</a></p>\n\n<h2>If they deny owing the money</h2>\n\n<p>If they deny owing the money, and you&rsquo;re owed less than \u20ac2,000, you can use the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://e-justice.europa.eu/content_small_claims-42-en.do\" title=\"European Small Claims Procedure\">European Small Claims procedure.</a></p>\n\n<p>For larger sums of money, you may have to use the national court system, and should get legal advice:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://legaladviserfinder.justice.gov.uk/AdviserSearch.do\" title=\"find a legal adviser\">find a legal adviser (England and Wales)</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.lawscot.org.uk/wcm/lssservices/find_a_solicitor/Core/directory.aspx\" title=\"find a solicitor (Scotland)\">find a solicitor (Scotland)</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Find out more about <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://hmctsformfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/GetLeaflet.do?court_leaflets_id=1048\" title=\"making a cross-border claim in the EU\">making a cross-border claim in the EU.</a></p>\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Court claims, debt and bankruptcy","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes recovering debts, registering for bankruptcy and as a creditor","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=justice%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice/court-claims-debt-bankruptcy"},"parent":{"title":"Crime, justice and the law","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Legal processes, courts and the police","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=justice","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Make a court claim for money","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/make-court-claim-for-money.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/make-court-claim-for-money","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"1921","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Make a money claim online","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/make-money-claim-online.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/make-money-claim-online","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"2004","business_proposition":true}}]]],"parts":null}